{"word":"Lead","slug":"lead","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Lead</b> A mineral<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=10'>Exo 15:10</a><br/> Purified by fire<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=22'>Num 31:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=29'>Jer 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=18'>Eze 22:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=20'>Eze 22:20</a><br/> Used in making inscriptions on stone<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=19&verse=24'>Job 19:24</a><br/> Lead-founder<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=29'>Jer 6:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=18'>Eze 22:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=20'>Eze 22:20</a><br/> Trade in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=12'>Eze 27:12</a><br/> Used for weighing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=5&verse=8'>Zec 5:8</a>"}]}